Context: The Sally Horsfall Eaton Academic Resource Centre at Toronto Metropolitan (Ryerson) is located at 99 Gerrard Street East in Toronto, Ontario, M5G 2A7. Their contact information includes a phone number, (416) 415-5000 ext. 2977, and TTY number, 1-877-515-5559. The ARC floor plan and Toronto Metropolitan maps can be found on their website. The nearest subway station is Dundas. For land acknowledgment information and to stay updated on application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and more, visitors are encouraged to sign up. Additional contact details include a phone number, 416-415-2000, TTY number, 1-877-515-5559, and an email address, ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The website contains information subject to change without notice and should not be considered a representation, offer or warranty.
